stimulusHtml: What, if anything, is printed as a result of executing the code segment?

features.html:
Consider the following code segment.

 

String[][] words = {{"Hello,", "Hi,", "Hey,"}, 
                    {"it's", "it is", "it really is"}, 
                    {"nice", "great", "a pleasure"}, 
                    {"to", "to get to", "to finally"}, 
                    {"meet", "see", "catch up with"}, 
                    {"you", "you again", "you all"}}; 
 
for (int j = 0; j < words.length; j++) 
{ 
   for (int k = 0; k < words[j].length; k++) 
   { 
      if (k == 1) 
      { 
         System.out.print(words[j][k] + " "); 
      } 
   } 
}

choicesHtml: Nothing is printed due to an  ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException.
Hello, it’s nice to meet you
Hey, it really is a pleasure to finally catch up with you all
Hi, it is great to get to see you again
